---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Yang Yu" description="Learn more about Yang Yu">
  <div class="about-content">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <p>
      Hello! I'm Yang Yu, a developer passionate about creating meaningful digital experiences.
    </p>
    <p>
      Welcome to my personal space on the web where I share my thoughts, projects, and journey in technology.
    </p>
    
    <h2>What I Do</h2>
    <p>
      I enjoy working on various projects ranging from web development to exploring new technologies.
      This blog serves as a place to document my learning and share insights with others.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>
      Feel free to reach out if you'd like to connect or collaborate on interesting projects.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  h1 {
    color: #1f2937;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #3b82f6;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  h2 {
    color: #374151;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
</style> 